import subprocess, sys
ok=True
for i in range(1,10):
    p = subprocess.run(['python3','solution.py'], input=str(i)+'\n', text=True, capture_output=True)
    out = p.stdout.strip()
    expected = str(i)*i

sys.exit(0 if ok else 1)
